1. https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/blob/v2.3.2/src/Fixer/Phpdoc/PhpdocSeparationFixer.php#L170

A method that find itself the newline style:

https://github.com/FriendsOfPHP/PHP-CS-Fixer/blob/v2.3.2/src/DocBlock/Line.php#L134

